{"tid":941101,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)獨闖龍潭 火星幽靈 關鍵密碼 刺客戰場","createTime":"2018-12-14T13:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T20:28:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b63d02f6176c7da7636802c77b7f598dd64dc717","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=891cd2a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1f239f3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=721884a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d9/Commandoposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd9%2FCommandoposter.jpg&h=27a48d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.123kubo.org/Uploads/vod/2018-07-18/5b4ee83a4a88b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.123kubo.org%2FUploads%2Fvod%2F2018-07-18%2F5b4ee83a4a88b.jpg&h=aceb074a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://photos1.blogger.com/blogger/2316/543/1600/px_flen0042521002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotos1.blogger.com%2Fblogger%2F2316%2F543%2F1600%2Fpx_flen0042521002.jpg&h=e4df1c15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/luketsu/1362020957-1987790984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fluketsu%2F1362020957-1987790984.jpg&h=fbcc82c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.約翰&middot;馬特里克斯（阿諾&middot;史瓦辛格飾）是三角洲部隊的一位退役上校，他得知自己在部隊中的上司富蘭克林&middot;科比少將以及小隊中的所有戰友都被一夥來歷不明的僱傭兵所殺。原來這夥人以前也是三角洲部隊成員，因為過於殘暴而被開除出隊伍後懷恨在心決心報復。他們接下來又偷襲了馬特里克斯的家，綁架了他的女兒簡妮<br />\n<br />\n2.故事發生在公元2176的火星，這個紅色星球已成為地球人口飽和後的移居地。共有64萬居民生活、工作在火星的各地，開發那裡豐富的自然資源。一小隊特警授命前往一個礦場小鎮，去押解在囚的極度罪犯威廉姆斯（艾斯&middot;古巴飾），並遣送回人類在火星上的中心城市。梅蘭妮（娜塔莎&middot;亨斯屈奇飾）就是這個小隊的副指揮官。可她萬萬沒有料到，這個小鎮的人類由於採礦而觸動了火星上的遠古文明遺址，並喚醒了一直埋藏著的火星幽靈。這些幽靈要摧毀任何生存在火星上的人類了！當特警隊在一無所知中抵達這個偏遠小鎮時，發現這裡除了被鎖藏在監獄裡的罪犯外已經沒有任何人生存了，為了活命，梅蘭妮和特警隊員只有和極度重犯聯手抗敵....<br />\n<br />\n3.二十年前發生了一件被稱為堪薩斯城洗牌（聲東擊西之意）的事：馬克斯偶然知曉一場賽馬比賽造假的內幕，於是從黑社會借了一大筆錢押注於內定的冠軍賽馬「幸運數字斯萊文」。但這一情況被黑社會發現，狙擊了內定的冠軍騎手，導致馬克斯無法還債。隨後，黑社會殺害了馬克斯及其妻子，以警告他人不能用黑社會的錢去投機。馬克斯年幼的兒子亨利被交給古德凱特去處死，但古德凱特良心發現，未殺亨利，反將其撫養長大<br />\n<br />\n4.Robert Rath是業界排名第一的殺手，但他卻無法逃離15年前殺死好友Nicolai的罪惡感，於是決定再幹幾票就要收山。在執行任務途中，他發現自己的「標靶」被一名年輕的殺手Miguel Bain槍殺。兩人幾次槍戰，Rath知道了Bain是自己的崇拜者，同時盼望能幹掉他而成為天下第一<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6ccd9fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=naVV2UsrwoB%2BRHXBd48YuQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=daf4e515\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1008d661b3d4b9ee18219034dfb1c9c0a2069a9b","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59a2953e6fd984d26b9b05a191d762c837a18ce","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c5f9f824333cdc63482a7332f88e6ecccfeb91","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cad41f36664dc3f710f448c4a376268ea98fd70","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ed8269be68c974b80dcb10de22bd2f9fdb9f22","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a9a9f3b6ecfc6cff0a0e0f6af2867f56c458f","tid":941101,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB